\fs28 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Long Position (Long)
\f1\b0 \cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 \'a0\'96 The buying of a currency pair with the expectation of a rise in value. When buying, a trade is executed at the Ask price.\cf5 \cb1 \strokec5 \

\f0\b \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Short Position (Short)
\f1\b0 \cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 \'a0\'96 The selling of a currency pair with the anticipation of making a profit as the price drops in value. When selling, a trade is executed at the Bid price.\cf5 \cb1 \strokec5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa80\partightenfactor0

