\f0\b \cf4 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec4 Buy Stop
\f1\b0 \cf5 \strokec5 \'a0\'96 a Buy order set at a price above the current price, and is filled as a market order when reached.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
